4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person eating asparagus##7
5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
6. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
7. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person who likes green is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
