4. the fan of d&b is between the indonesian and the cottage house##2
5. the nigerian is not the fan of r&b##6
6. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
7. the cottage house is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the modern house and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
