The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, bike, boat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cricket, parkour, sailing
1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the fan of punk is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is sailing##7
8. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
9. the fan of blues is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is cricket##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | punk    | blues    | metal     |
| Transport   | quad-bike | airplane | boat  | bike |
| Sport         | sailing    | parkour | baseball | cricket   |

